248
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,120
organizations are organizations.

249
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:27,820
The problem with giving organizations

250
00:13:27,820 --> 00:13:30,460
such powers as CIA has

251
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:33,020
is on the positive side,

252
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,340
you can accomplish great things.

253
00:13:34,420 --> 00:13:35,200
On the negative side,

254
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,660
you can do very bad things.

255
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:39,040
And especially when you're doing them in secret.

256
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:40,720
You have some interesting stories

257
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,060
