259
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:46,500
giving Bush advice,

260
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,060
giving Cheney advice.

261
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:51,560
Do you want to give a couple of examples there

262
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:54,540
