263
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:57,120
or advised in kind of very high up

264
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:59,120
American national security contexts?

265
00:13:59,380 --> 00:13:59,400
Right.

266
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:03,780
My career breaks down into three phases, really.

267
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,640
The first phase was between

268
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:09,620
