276
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,320
And I became really good at that.

277
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:24,500
Then suddenly, boom,

278
00:14:25,380 --> 00:14:27,040
almost 10 years into my career,

279
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,420
we get with almost exactly,

280
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:29,480
we get hit with 9-11.

281
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:31,160
And after 9-11,

282
00:14:31,420 --> 00:14:33,960
I was actually in language training

283
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,240
