289
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,260
I had been on the director,

290
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:45,780
director of CIA staff

291
00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:47,820
the year before preceding 9-11

292
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:49,940
