295
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:53,460
So I was a staffer

296
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:55,520
supporting the director,

297
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:56,840
who was a good friend of mine,

298
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:57,700
wonderful director,

299
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:58,180
in my mind,

300
00:14:58,260 --> 00:14:58,800
George Tenet.

301
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,980
And we knew that we were

302
00:15:00,980 --> 00:15:02,200
going to be hit 9-11.

303
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:05,340
We didn't know where.

304
00:15:06,500 --> 00:15:09,580
And I'm not in the school of belief,

305
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:11,100
and I know that it's a valid way

306
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:11,640
to think of it,

307
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:12,360
