308
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:13,440
Well, we failed because

309
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,780
we allowed the attack to happen,

310
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:16,600
but could we have prevented it?

311
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:18,000
I think that's in ways

312
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,340
