313
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:20,880
because I don't think

314
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:22,460
we could have prevented 9-11.

315
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:24,120
We just have to give the credit

316
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,420
to the terrorists,

317
00:15:25,580 --> 00:15:26,720
to Osama bin Laden terrorists.

318
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,340
But it changed everyone's lives

319
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:29,360
and future of the world,

320
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:30,940
and that was the intent

321
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:31,560
of the terrorists,

322
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:32,740
including my little life.

323
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:33,900
So they pulled me

324
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:34,980
from my language training,

325
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:36,020
