00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:43,320
which was to stop terrorists

331
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,700
from acquiring biological

332
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:45,880
or nuclear weapons.

333
00:15:47,300 --> 00:15:48,600
I mean, that's a, yeah,

334
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:51,480
if the future of the world

335
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,760
hinges on any job,

336
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:53,580
that's the job.

337
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:55,800
I did say to George Tenet,

338
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:56,760
who I already knew well

339
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:57,220
because I'd been

340
00:15:57,220 --> 00:15:58,060
on his senior staff,

341
00:15:58,140 --> 00:15:58,800
I said, George,

342
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,000
isn't there anybody

343
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,760
better than me for this?

344
00:16:02,220 --> 00:16:02,900
How did he respond

345
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:04,160
when he said, you know,

346
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,060
hey, can't you find

347
00:16:05,060 --> 00:16:05,980
anybody better than me?

348
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,300
Oh, classic George Tenet

349
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:07,580
response.

350
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:08,940
Like I said, great leader,

351
00:16:09,180 --> 00:16:10,540
a great leader of men and women.

352
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:12,560
He said, hey,

353
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:14,080
I got worse news for you.

354
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:15,280
You don't have any people yet.

355
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:17,060
I went from three people

356
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:17,740
at that meeting

357
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:19,360
that had been assigned to me

358
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,760
to 150 over the next weeks.

359
00:16:22,100 --> 00:16:23,000
And then he said,

360
00:16:23,060 --> 00:16:24,880
but you were behind the eight ball,

361
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:26,020
and he explained why,

362
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,140
which is still classified,

363
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,060
which meant there was

364
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:29,580
a plausible reason

365
00:16:29,580 --> 00:16:30,240
