367
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:32,580
a nuclear weapon,

368
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,100
which was,

369
00:16:33,460 --> 00:16:34,600
I can say the basics,

370
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:36,260
