385
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:57,100
We can't let them score on this.

386
00:16:57,180 --> 00:16:58,700
We can't let them do this one time

387
00:16:58,700 --> 00:16:59,760
and take out the White House

388
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:00,920
